To run on QEMU:
Download qemu-0.15.0

Patch the file qemu-0.15.0/target-lm32/translate.c:
  comment out the line that says
  cpu_abort(dc->env, "fetching nop sequence\n");

Build qemu with
./configure --target-list=lm32-softmmu
make

Change to qemu-0.15.0/lm32-softmmu directory
Run the following command
./qemu-system-lm32 -nographic -M lm32-uclinux -pflash PATH/TO/flash.img

